summary: The graph shows the cold storage investment volume and rent pressures in general logistics for select cities from 2010 to 2023. The investment volume varies significantly, with Shanghai and Nantong having the highest volumes, while Sanya, Nanjing, and Shenzhen have lower volumes. Rent pressures in general logistics also show variations, with Shanghai and Nantong experiencing the highest pressures, while Sanya, Nanjing, and Shenzhen have lower pressures.
